flowchart TB
    %% External Interface
    Cursor[Cursor IDE] -->|MCP Protocol<br/>stdio transport| MCPServer[MCP Server<br/>15 Tools Exposed]
    
    %% MCP Server Layer 1: Structural Queries
    MCPServer --> Layer1[Layer 1: Structural Queries<br/>Fast graph operations<br/>&lt;100ms response]
    Layer1 --> RSSGraph[In-Memory RSS Graph<br/>Loaded from AI-DOC state]
    
    %% MCP Server Layer 2: Context Assembly
    MCPServer --> Layer2[Layer 2: Context Assembly<br/>Graph + source code<br/>100-500ms response]
    Layer2 --> Layer1
    Layer2 --> FileSystem[File System<br/>Source code files]
    
    %% File Watching & RECON Pipeline
    Watchdog[Watchdog Orchestrator<br/>Coordinates file watching<br/>and RECON triggering] --> FileWatcher[File Watcher<br/>chokidar FSWatcher<br/>Monitors project files]
    FileWatcher -->|file changes| EditQueue[Edit Queue Manager<br/>Debouncing &amp; Coalescing<br/>500ms manual / 2s AI edits]
    EditQueue -->|stable changes| TxDetector[Transaction Detector<br/>Multi-file edit detection<br/>3s transaction window]
    TxDetector -->|complete transaction| IncrementalRecon[Incremental RECON<br/>O changed files<br/>Updates AI-DOC state]
    IncrementalRecon -->|writes| AIDocState[AI-DOC State<br/>.ste/state/<br/>YAML slices on disk]
    AIDocState -->|loads| RSSGraph
    IncrementalRecon -->|notifies| MCPServer
    MCPServer -->|reloads context| RSSGraph
    
    %% Styling
    classDef external fill:#e1f5ff,stroke:#01579b,stroke-width:2px
